-- Starwood Property Deploys $271.9 Million in Capital for Loan Orginations
-- B y   J o A n n e   N o r t o n
-- 2010-12-28T12:37:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-28/starwood-property-deploys-271-9-million-in-capital-for-loan-orginations.html
Starwood Property Trust said it has
deployed $271.9 million of capital through three separate loan
originations: a $206 million first-mortgage loan, mezzanine loan
and bridge loan on a portfolio of 10 full-service hotels
throughout the U.S.; a $33.9 million first-mortgage and
mezzanine loan on a portfolio of U.S. drug stores; and a $32
million first-mortgage loan on a retail development in Vail,
Colorado.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
JoAnne Norton at 
 jnorton@bloomberg.net  